## 🌐 Project Overview
AgriChat is an AI-powered conversational assistant designed to support agricultural professionals and farmers with intelligent, real-time guidance.

## 🏗️ System Architecture
### Components
- IBM Watson Assistant
- Natural Language Processing Engine
- Cloud Infrastructure
- Data Storage System

### Workflow
1. User Input
2. Natural Language Processing
3. Intent Recognition
4. Response Generation
5. Output Delivery

## 🔧 Installation

### Prerequisites
- Python 3.8+
- IBM Cloud Account
- Watson Assistant Instance

### Step-by-Step Setup
```bash
# Clone Repository
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/AgriChat.git
cd AgriChat

# Create Virtual Environment
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate  # On Windows use `venv\Scripts\activate`

# Install Dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Configure Watson Assistant
python setup_watson.py
